Goa
Oct 19, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			A 64-year-old man was arrested for allegedly raping his minor niece in South Goa district, the police said today.

The accused, Kondlo Vithoba Velip, living in Morpirla village of Quepem taluka, allegedly confined the 10-year-old girl in a room at a house in his neighbourhood where he raped her yesterday, a police spokesman said.

The accused was immediately arrested, he said.

